fi.sorberIT
类 HandleInformation

java.lang.Object
  fi.sorberIT.HandleInformation

public class HandleInformation
extends java.lang.Object

HandleInformation is connected with the HibernateUtil class and MySAXHandler class. Through importing the HibernateUtil class, it can get the session. Through importing the MySAXHandler class, it can save the value of attributes and put them into database.

public void addInformation(java.lang.Object obj)
